trans-unit.source: Provides a dictionary for designer styles.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en ordliste for Spørringsutformer stiler.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the current dictionary instance from a XAML file at a specific resource location.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer gjeldende ordliste forekomst fra XAML filer på en bestemt ressurs-plassering.

trans-unit.source: Gets the sequence style stored in this <xref href="System.Activities.Core.Presentation.Themes.DesignerStylesDictionary"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter stilen sekvens lagret på denne <xref href="System.Activities.Core.Presentation.Themes.DesignerStylesDictionary"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Also, seals the sequence style if it is not already sealed.
trans-unit.target: Også stenger stilen sekvens hvis den allerede ikke er lukket.

trans-unit.source: The sequence style stored in this <xref href="System.Activities.Core.Presentation.Themes.DesignerStylesDictionary"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Stilen sekvens lagret på denne <xref href="System.Activities.Core.Presentation.Themes.DesignerStylesDictionary"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Attaches events and names to compiled content.
trans-unit.target: Knytter hendelser og navn til kompilerte innhold.

trans-unit.source: This interface is designed for use only by the markup compiler.
trans-unit.target: Dette grensesnittet er utviklet for Bruk bare av markup manuelt.
